\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"your support\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Digital Only $5/month Print & Digital $6/month MORE OPTIONS Already a subscriber?Log into hide this.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Digital\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"Only $5/month Print\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"Digital\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"$6/month MORE OPTIONS\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"Already a subscriber?Log\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing is considered one of the five elements of hip-hop culture, which celebrated its 51st birthday on Sunday, August 11, along with MCing, DJing, knowledge, and the visual art form graffiti.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9968041416206764, \"rank\": 0.003206104635845427, \"text\": \"DJing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the five elements\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop culture\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 628}, {\"ngram\": \"its 51st birthday\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"MCing\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"the visual art form\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"graffiti\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Paris Olympics that concluded on Sunday, for the first time, breakdancing was an Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The results reflect the globalization of hip-hop.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The results\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"the globalization\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The news mainstream media just does not cover.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The news mainstream media\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Racial justice journalism since 1909.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Racial justice journalism\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Philip Kim, also known as Phil Wizard, a native of Toronto, Canada, who was also raised in Vancouver, took home gold.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Kim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Kim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Kim\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 4.851793584992272e-12, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9999541933516956, \"rank\": 4.350310902732183e-05, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1