tp://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.20547151197447e-44, \"text\": \"James Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 2962, \"end\": 2971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Get_on_the_Good_Foot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Good Foot\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Get_on_the_Good_Foot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Get_on_the_Good_Foot\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"West African dances\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"grass dances\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2713}, {\"ngram\": \"other well-grounded movements\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"the Jitterbug/Lindy Hop\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"Huffing\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"Tap dance\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pabon is adamant that knowledge of these creative expressions will help young dancers understand the foundation of modern art forms.\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pabon\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"that knowledge\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"these creative expressions\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"young dancers\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"the foundation\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"modern art forms\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Mixed feelings from the start,\\\" Pabon, who was born in Spanish Harlem, said of his initial reaction when it was announced that breakdancing would be in the Paris Olympics \\\"I was delighted that our sacred dance and culture was, once again, acknowledged as being worthy of such a prestigious platform.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3410, \"e